      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row701538#s2",
      "text": "He has a recent    diagnosis of HIV ([**7-31**]), has C.diff with leukocytosis in 40s, adrenal    insufficiency, MDS(prbc and plt transfusion dependent), worsening    acidosis and renal failure due to ATN."
    },
